Package: staticdocs
Type: Package
Title: Make static html documentation for a package.
Description: Convert package rd files to static html pages, suitable for
    serving on a website.
Version: 0.1
Author: Hadley Wickham <h.wickham@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Hadley Wickham <h.wickham@gmail.com>
License: MIT
